Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.26,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(640,60)\fscy50\1vc(&HDCBDFF&,&HDCBDFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}{\t(0,100,\fscy150\fscx80)}{\t(100,200,\fscy100\fscx100)}甜甜蜜蜜的 暖心之愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.48,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(640,60)\fscy50\1vc(&HDCBDFF&,&HDCBDFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}{\t(0,100,\fscy150\fscx80)}{\t(100,200,\fscy100\fscx100)}LOVE 心跳心跳 Let’s say!
